오늘의 소소한 일상 💨
.
.
비 오는데 집앞에서 안들어가려는 복실이와 비를 흠뻑 맞고,
스타벅스 들려서 제일 좋아하는 화이트모카 한잔 사고.
건강검진 받으러 아침 일찍 병원에 다녀오고,
살이 쪘다 싶더니 또 빠지기 시작해서 스트레스 😢
.
노란머리에서 검정색으로 염색도 하고,
퇴근하는 오빠 기다리는 그저 여유로운 그런 하루있잖아:)
카페를 차릴까 애견미용을 차릴까 부모님이랑 오빠랑 고민도 하고,
집으로 돌아와서 소박한 일상 즐기던 그런 조용한 날.
비 오는데 하늘은 너무 예쁘고 집가는 발걸음이 가볍던 그런 하루 
.

. 
Jadi antara menu yang bamziaf sempat cuba Grilled Salmon Spaghetti (Portion dia mmg meriah, Salmon yg fresh & sedap) , Soft Shell Crab Tempura (Crab dia lembut, nasi dia wangi & enak) , Chocolate Cake with IceCream ( Cake dia sgt moist ) & The Cousin Milkshakes ( Hampa kena cuba ni, Salted Caramel dia mmg power!!)
.
Banyak lagi menu lain yang hampa boleh cuba & pastinya semua so shedapp tau! Harga dekat sini sgt affordable tau!! Jadi apa tunggu lagi cepat check out IG @garage51my untuk info lanjut!!

2022明治安田生命J1リーグ第27節
清水1 -0 京都

山原、松岡という好調を支えていたメンバーを欠く中で、予想以上に厳しい試合に。
京都は球際が激しく、特に前線の山崎がしっかりロングボールに身体を張っていて厄介でした。

しかし乾のスーパーゴールをDF陣はじめ全員で身体を張り、それでも撃たれたシュートは権田がストップ、見事守り切った勝利は残留争いの上でも、そしてチームの成長という面でも大きなものになりました！

乾は華やかな個人技より、ボールキープやトラップ、攻守のポジショニングといった基礎技術だけでも勝利に貢献してくれる選手という印象でしたが、今日のゴールは期待値をさらに上げてくれました。
明日清水銀座に行けば色々ご馳走してもらえそう😁
もちろん起点になった立田、競り合いを落としてくれた瑛ちゃん、アシストのカルリ、みんな素晴らしかった！

最後に。次のホーム湘南戦も勝って、またオレンジサマーナイトが観られますように。

第一次睡露宿袋，紀錄

D1 鈴鳴東鞍（森林營地）
實測一晚沒有被動物騷擾，露宿袋也沒有反潮，晚上從樹林間的縫隙可看到天氣很好，有零碎的星點，睡起來滿爽的。

D2 無明池（稜線營地）
稜線上的風比較大，約7點進帳篷，霧氣從山谷往上升，晚上8點多左右內部就開始反潮，睡前很擔心睡袋濕掉後會被冷醒，但還好半夜霧氣散掉，睡得也很好。

凌晨3:21分醒來，滑了一下手機沒網路，就躺在露宿袋裡看著天空的星星發呆，一開始看到天邊一顆流星滑過，原以為是看錯，接著陸續看到四顆流星，看了半小時，很滿足的去睡覺，早上突然驚醒，看著旁邊的景色發呆了一陣子，之後速速叫帳篷裡的孫起床看日出

第一次在稜線上起床，躺著看日出的感覺非常讚。

溪邊蟲太多，還是睡帳篷好😅
但因為太熱把外帳拆掉，通風

Can we just take a moment to appreciate the beauty of the @coolermaster.uk MASTERAIR MA610P ARGB Cooler⁉️ swipe 👈 and check out some close up shots from my photoshoot this morning!

Ok, so this isn’t an official PC build for the channel, I built this stunning little rig on my favourite open chassis (@kompcase Magnus) purposely to power up and showcase this cooler! Was it worth the time and effort? Totally! 

If RGB and air cooling is your thing then say no more! The MA610P is cooled by two Sickleflow fans which provide leading cooling performance and also look stunning at the same time, that’s a double win in my book! 

Socket support for Intel LGA 2066 right to 1366 socket, and of course AMD AM4, AM3, AM2 and FM. This thing moves more than enough air to keep performance optimal. 

So, double tap this post if you’re a fan of RGB! Also, leave a comment and let me know what you think of the MASTERAIR MA610P! 😁👇

Big thanks to @coolermaster.uk for the support as always! 💜

🍳 Renu By Fer Coffee 🥞

Hola foodies! Hoy se inauguró el divino espacio de la cafetería de Renu by Fer y por supuesto que no podía faltar nuestra reseña 🥳💖

🍳🤤 Renu by Fer Coffee es un nuevo lugar para probar desayunos estilo brunch, con un toque único que solo Renu tiene. 

🎂✨ La reina del conejito Turín que nos ha deleitado con pasteles y postres deliciosos y divinos, ahora viene a innovar con un concepto de platillos dulces y salados que no se pueden perder!

💖🍽 Chilaquiles Renu con Pollo | 💵 $180
Que platillo tan mas divino, se ve tan precioso que no quería arruinarlo jaja 
La salsa rosa es algo realmente intrigante y delicioso, pensaba que tendría un sabor dulce pero no fue así; tiene un sabor cremoso y con un toque de picante perfecto, que combina con los totopos, pollo, crema y queso.

🍦🍓 Parfait de fruta | 💵 $115
Un delicioso preparado de yogurt griego, suave y cremoso, con fresas frescas, miel y granola, algo dulce y fresco para acompañar el desayuno.

🧁🍓 Cupcake de red velvet | 💰 $55
Y no puede faltar en nuestra visita la delicia de postres que Renu tiene en su carta, una de sus especialidades es el red velvet hecho cupcake con una cobertura cremosa y el toque acido de la fresa, completamente exquisito. 

☕️🥛 Latte Frío | 💰 $58

📍 Visítalos en Av. Araucarias #296 antes del parque el huarache 
📲 WhatsApp 228 854 3070
🏍 Pide a domicilio con costo extra

Makka Darzi Mosque, Khairabad, UP

According to historians, the "Makka Darzi," also known as the "Makka Jaamadar," was built in 1835 by a man called Makka who was a close friend of the then-King Nasir-ud-din Haider of Oudh. It is reported that Nasir-ud-thirst din's for European clothing was satisfied by Makka, the sole tailor in the entire realm.

According to some historians, Makka is thought to have learned the intricate details of English dressmaking from the king's five favorite European acquaintances. He was so skilled at what he did that he could charge whatever he wanted for designing and making a unique outfit that met Nasir-ud-din Haider's requirements.

Perhaps because of his close relationship with the monarch, he asked for a large sum of money to be used to build the complex that houses this mosque.

Its combination and representation of the Nawabi-Mughal-gothic architectural styles has led some historians to label it as one of the most magnificent monuments. Viewers are delighted by the exquisite roof inlay work and the robust stucco work.

Currently, the dilapidated building is a hotspot for crime and is occupied by around 200 squatters. According to historians in the city, it would be a significant step to preserve the dilapidated building, which is one of the most significant aspects of the history of the former Oudh.

🪐 LA TÊTE DANS LES ÉTOILES 🪐

Samedi, pour la nuit des étoiles, nous avons choisi d'aller les observer depuis le @museeairespace du Bourget. 

En plus de l'observation des étoiles et planètes avec des télescopes de compèt', le programme  était bien rempli 😁: simulation de marche sur la lune, entraînement pour l'espace, visite d'un Concorde et d'un Boeing 747, ....
Pour la touche #disney (il faut toujours qu'il y en ai une 🤣), une petite expo était consacrée au dernier film Pixar : Buzz L'Eclair 🌠

Sans oublier, la découverte de ce musée incroyable qui a littéralement conquis Théo : j'ai peut être un futur Thomas Pesquet à la maison 😉.
Nous y retournerons avec grand plaisir, en journée, pour découvrir les parties que nous n'avons pas eu le temps de visiter 🌕.

Vamos de lembranças? Há 1 ano atrás Kylie, Travis e Stormi viajavam à NYC por 24hr para comparecer a evento beneficente da Parson’s School em Nova York. 

Travis foi homenageado na 72° premiação por suas contribuições com moda, design, empreendedorismo, artes e justiça social. 

Após passarem juntos pelo tapete como uma bela família, Travis realizou um discurso na premiação, onde o rapper se declarou para Stormi e Kylie.

— “Stormi, eu te amo e esposa, eu te amo”.

Importante acrescentar que logo após a família deixar o evento, Kylie postou uma foto abraçada com Travis em seu feed, que parou a internet! 🔥

O casal ainda não era assumido e nem possuiam vestígios de relacionamento na época, desde o término em 2019.

Para apoiar ainda mais seu maridão, Kylie fez questão de postar um TikTok pós evento, mostrando detalhes da rotina de preparativos para comparecer ao lado de Travis no tapete vermelho do Parson's.

Was ist wohl die beste Reaktion auf Leute, die dir erzählen wollen, wie du zu sein hast? 

Richtig: Ein feistes "Leck mich am Arsch" Grinsen. 

Natürlich, bis zu einem gewissen Grad aufeinander Rücksicht nehmen und uns an einige Konventionen halten ist gut. Schließlich wünschen wir uns das auch selbst von anderen und es ist schließlich dazu da, damit wir Menschen halbwegs miteinander auskommen. Wir (mehr oder weniger) sozialen Wesen brauchen schließlich einander. 

Aber eine Gesellschaft besteht aus Individuen. Und so sehr wir auch gesellschaftliche Rücksicht üben sollten, der Einzelne sollte ebenfalls gewürdigt und respektiert werden. 

Und solange du weder dir noch jemand anderem schadest: sei DU. 

Wenn dir also jemand erzählt, du seist nicht "gut genug"... Siehe oben. 

Habt einen schönen Tag. ☀
